<div align="center">
<p><strong>1.Payment information:</strong><br />
                we prefer western   union,money gram and T/T. If you send the money by western union or money gram,   please kindly let us know the following information: first name and last name   you write on the bank receipt, and exact amount you make, and MTCN(money   transfer control number), if you pay by T/T, please send us the bank receipt by   fax or email, after you do the payment. <br />
                <br />
                <strong>2.Delivery time:</strong><br />
                If the goods you order are in our stock, We will send the   goods within two working days after we get the payment confirmation from the bank. Once we ship out the goods, we will provide you with the tracking numbers   for tracking. Normally, it will take 5-7 working days for the goods to travel to Western Europe and USA, 7-9 working days to North America and 9-10 working days   to other areas. <br />
                <br />
                <strong>3.Price:</strong><br />
                1)All prices listed in the website include express shipping cost to your door.<br />
                2)All WHOLESALE prices   on site are in US dollars or Euro.<br />
                3)The price are effective for Europe,   Asia, North America, if the goods need?shipping to South America, Africa, You   must add Others for the extra shipping cost.<br />
                4)The price we quoted,,   referring to ship the goods by express, if you prefer other ways of delivery, we   will quote you again.<br />
                <br />
                <strong>4.Product:</strong><br />
                All of our products   are produced by the factory and they are of top quality.<br />
                <br />
                <strong>5.Shippment: </strong><br />
                we handle all kinds of   shipping ways according to the customer request, such as by sea, by air, by   express(EMS, DHL, TNT, FEDEX ,SODEXI,UPS). We also can handle drop shipping to the customer directly, but the price is a little higher than normal shipping. In   order to guarantee you can receive the goods correctly, please write your   address , receiver, and telephone number in details and clearly. <br />
                <br />
                <strong>6.OEM:</strong><br />
                We also can produce the goods according to   the customers request of all kinds, such as change logo and change the   color, size and material according to customers request, if the order is 60 pairs or more. In this case, we can arrange to delivery within10-12 working   days. <br />
                <br />
                <strong>7.Mini order:</strong><br />
                The minimum order of our shoes   is 6 pairs(others is 6 too) per style. but we accept the small order such as 1  or 2pairs for the new customers in order to let the customers to take a look at   the top quality of our shoes and promptly service. </p>
